1) cd fluffos-2.9-ds2.08
2) ./configure nm3
3) make
4) make install
5) cd ../bin
6) Create local config from project root:
     ./mud.sh init-config
   Or copy mudos.cfg.example to mudos.cfg and set absolute mudlib/binary paths.

7) From project root: ./mud.sh doctor && ./mud.sh start
8) telnet localhost 1122

Notes:
- Step 2 only prepares the build; you must run make and make install separately.
- Default player port is 1122 (not 2701).
- See ../../INSTALL.md and ../../RUNNING.md for full documentation.

Have fun!
